### ========================
### TESTS SPÉCIFIQUES SMS OTP
### ========================

### Test: SMS OTP - Envoi et validation complète
# @name smsOTPFULL
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phone": "{{smsTestPhone}}",
    "pin": "1957",
    "full_name": "SMS Test User",
    "email": "sms_test{{$randomInt}}@example.com",
    "city": "Nouakchott"
}

### Test: Vérifier que SMS a été envoyé (OTP envoyé automatiquement après register)
# @name checkSMSOTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/otp/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phone": "{{smsTestPhone}}",
    "purpose": "register"
}

### Test: Valider OTP SMS reçu
# @name validateSMSOTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/otp/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phone": "{{smsTestPhone}}",
    "code": "{{devOtpCode}}",
    "purpose": "register"
}

### Test: Login après validation SMS OTP
# @name loginAfterSMS
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phone": "{{smsTestPhone}}",
    "pin": "1957"
}

